title: Nice! One bedroom Apartment in Classic Building
posting_body: ['Nice One!', 'Quiet one bedroom apartment.', 'Classic old-world moldings and details.', 'Updated Kitchen', 'Updated Bathroom', 'Washer and Dryer on site.', 'Great location close to the Panhandle, all the great restaurants and cafes in Nopa, Golden Gate Park, UCSF, and USF.', 'Nice main room with historic moldings, details, and cool stained glass windows and light fixtures.', 'Quiet bedroom overlooks a rarely used backyard.', 'Owner pays Hot Water, Water, and Garbage included in the rent.', 'This is a savings of about $100/month compared to apts where the tenant pays for utilities.', ' Tenants pay PG&E and Cable/Phone/WiFi if desired.', 'Cats ok with additional security deposit.', 'We comply with all Fair Housing Laws.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', '$35.00 Application Fee', 'Easy to show.', 'Just Text Charles Post, Broker', 'CA DRE License #01421132', 'We comply with all Fair Housing Laws']
